  "rationale": "Order follows the brief's scroll: an inverse hero bookend, then an editorial primary/panel run. The hero adapts boundary-straddle-headline \u2014 a full-bleed timber photo with a colossal WOODWAVE display title straddling the rail/photo seam (the single sanctioned text-on-media + accent), a panel rail, and a flat medium scrim carrying keyword columns. About and Heritage use giant ghost words ('ABOUT', '1941 / 2023') behind anchored/staggered statements as the brief requests; the gallery showcase reuses the full-bleed counter-band with a static counter and marginal caption (no controls, no overlay text). The required banded section adapts seam-straddle-portrait for the mission moment \u2014 a photo band over a light panel band with a portrait straddling the hard seam (sanctioned media-over-seam, no text sanction needed). Curator quote and visit info reuse project split patterns; newsletter is an underline-only form (no boxed inputs, no buttons); footer carries slash-nav and socials. Every non-hero section stays on primary/panel with zero accent, honoring single-accent and no-cards-on-cream via open collage and stat-block."
}
